SET linkedIn = CASE 
  WHEN name = 'Georg Blascheck' THEN 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/georg-blascheck-11b261296'
  WHEN name = 'Bibian Pacayra Bock' THEN 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/bibian-pacayra-498766330'

WHERE name IN ('Georg Blascheck', 'Bibian Pacayra Bock', 'Ma.Engela Rose Pacayra Espares');
